data.description: ENTICING ON ESTEY! Welcome home to this charming 2 bed, 2 1/2 bath, ranch style house in Beaverton. This well kept property with 2 1?2 acres boasts a large pond and offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and fun. It’s a cozy home with a large living room for entertaining and family fun and also features a wood burning stove and a large primary bedroom with a huge walk-in closet. One side of this spacious house has a living area, bedroom, and half bath that will seem like a second living space! There is a 35’x24’ detached 2 car garage and plenty of space outside for fun! This home is a gem and it's ready for you, don’t let this one get away!
